OL,3,CCalls for more support as energy costs
OL,4,C'crippling' small businesses
OL,6,FThe owner of Taunton Independent
OL,7,FMarket has said energy costs are
OL,8,F'crippling' small traders and they
OL,9,Fneed a lot more support from the
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FThe saw various announcements aimed at
OL,13,Fhelping small businesses, including a
OL,14,Fraise on the threshold for VAT
OL,15,Fregistration, fuel duty being frozen
OL,16,Fand recovery loans to allow small
OL,17,Ffirms to invest and grow.
