OL,4,C'crippling' small businesses
OL,6,FBut Michelle Beck, whose event takes
OL,7,Fplace regularly on Castle Green in
OL,8,FSomerset's county town, said she wants
OL,9,Fto see more done.
OL,11,FMichelle said: "Electricity costs are
OL,12,Fabsolutely crippling some of these
OL,13,Ftraders and it's doubling costs.
OL,15,F"I'd also like to see the VAT
OL,16,Fthreshold lifted a little bit. I would
OL,17,Fvery much like small businesses just
OL,18,Flooked after a bit more because
OL,19,Fthey're a very important part of the
OL,20,Fcommunity."
